  "title": "Weekly Pay Sales Executive – Immediate Hire!!",
  "description": "<h3>⚡ <strong>Sales Executive – Weekly Pay, No Experience Needed</strong></h3><p>Looking for a job that doesn’t overcomplicate things?<br />We train you, support you, and <strong>pay you every week</strong>. Easy.</p><p>🗣️ What You’ll Be Doing</p><ul><li><p>Talk to customers and introduce products/services</p></li><li><p>Learn sales skills step by step (<strong>training included</strong>)</p></li><li><p>Turn conversations into commissions 💰</p></li><li><p>Work with an energetic team in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Build confidence and people skills that last</p></li></ul><p>📚 Training Included</p><ul><li><p><strong>Full training from Day 1</strong></p></li><li><p>No sales experience required</p></li><li><p>Coaching and on-the-job support provided</p></li></ul><p>💸 What You Get</p><ul><li><p><strong>WEEKLY PAYOUT 💵</strong></p></li><li><p>Fast hiring & immediate start</p></li><li><p>Basic pay + commission + incentives</p></li><li><p>Great entry role for students, fresh grads & career switchers</p></li></ul><p>👀 Who Fits This Role</p><ul><li><p>Friendly, motivated, and eager to learn</p></li><li><p>Comfortable talking to people (or willing to try)</p></li><li><p>Positive mindset and good work ethic</p></li></ul><p><strong>Learn the skills. Make the sales. Get paid weekly.</strong><br />Apply now — limited spots available 🔥</p>",
